# Draft:Kingalcena

Kingalcena
A content creator recognized for his work in fashion and lifestyle. His videos showcase men's street style and outfit inspiration. He became active on instagram 2021. He has done modeling for brands like H&M and old navy
About
Kingalcena Birth name Steph "SJ" born January 2nd, 2000 (age 25) Occupations YouTuber  Songwriter Influencer Years active 2021 - present
SJ known professionally as Kingalcena
is an American
Model,  content creator, and Influencer He is known for men's street fashion. He has worked with Gunna and Tyler The Creator as well as '''Wiz Khalifa's Taylor Gang clothing brand.
Early life
SJ also known as Kingalcena, is a dynamic and versatile performer who shines as an actor, singer/songwriter, and digital content creator. At just 25 years old, he has established himself as an exceptionally adaptable artist, captivating young audiences with his engaging presence and unwavering commitment to his art.
Career
Originating from Miami, FL,  Kingalcena was predominantly raised by his mother, who encouraged his creative talents from an early age. As a young boy, he was presented with an opportunity to audition for a Disney series, but he had to turn it down due to the inability to finance a trip to Los Angeles. Maintaining a positive outlook,  Kingalcena promised himself that he would one day travel to Los Angeles to chase his aspirations.
Kingalcena is also a popular and prolific content creator.
Personal life
Kingalcena is a chirstian. He has deep passion for bible study and maintained a strong faith in God. He began learning to play the piano and developed a fondness for playing musical instruments. His affection for music know no bounds.
